  "name": "Aboleth Curse",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/horror-eerie-1.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your mind is marked by aboleth tampering, either as a result of a close encounter with one of these creatures while you were a child, or even through an ancestor, close family member, or one of your sisters or brothers in faith—this associate’s interaction with the aboleths may be all that it takes to infect you. You take a –2 penalty on saving throws against mind-affecting effects and add @Compendium[pf1.spells.tjog6bufg5b08lvq]{Charm Person} and @Compendium[pf1.spells.3ntxp3zun1j9mf0m]{Hypnotism} to your list of 1st-level oracle spells known.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, add @Compendium[pf1.spells.27o3msobhyghmfid]{Minor Image} to your list of 2nd-level oracle spells known.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, add @Compendium[pf1.spells.5ll7q13p0skbgonc]{Modify Memory} to your list of 4th-level oracle spells known.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, add @Compendium[pf1.spells.fxwycv6d7xwzua4t]{Veil} to your list of 6th-level oracle spells known.</p>"
    },
